Class ServerController

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.ServerController

  • public class ServerController
extends java.lang.Object
    ServerController class a controller for the server gui that have 3 text fields(port , DB root ,DB password) and 4 buttons connect , reset, exit and connect to DB(hidden and appears if the user insert wrong input about the database) to reconnect to it .
    Author:
    yana irani
